title: KENNEAS Humane Mouse Traps & Mice Traps Washable Reusable Live Catch and Release Mice, Mouse, Field Mouse & Rodent Catchers for Indoors Outdoors, Pets and Children Friendly (4 Pack)
features: 【0.1S CAPTURE】: The KENNEAS mouse traps boasts a highly sensitive pedal mechanism. With the slightest touch from a mouse, the spring door snaps shut immediately, capturing it securely in just 0.1s

【CHILD AND PET FRIENDLY】:Our mice trap is free from poisons and glue, with no pinch points or discomfort-causing components, ensuring safety for children and pets. It prevents contact with mice and their remnants,reducing disease risk, making it an ideal choice for families

【100% HUMANE】Humane mouse traps does not harm or kill the captured mice. It features an integrated bait box for providing water and food, and the housing is equipped with 66 ventilation holes, allowing the mice to live 3-5 days inside
【NOTE】: This mouse trap measures 7 * 7.2 cm and is only suitable for mice weighing no more than 150g and of a smaller size. Larger mice may not be caught effectively

【REUSABLE】: Designed for multiple uses, humane mouse traps for indoors-outdoors comes with a dedicated cleaning brush. Following the release of a captured mouse, simply clean and disinfect the trap to ready it for the next use

【EASY OPERATION】: This mousetrap offers straightforward operation: just place food in the bait box, open the spring door, and position it in areas with frequent mouse activity. It effectively captures mice and is ideal for use in home, kitchen, garage, restaurant, and supermarket
